data.description: Welcome to your future homestead! This fixer-upper cabin on approximately 2 acres is waiting for your personal touch. 2 bedrooms and 2 baths downstairs with an upstairs loft for additional sleeping space or office. Although in need of TLC, this property holds potential for your creative transformation.  Less than 1 mile to boat ramp and public access on the Little Red River at Winkley Shoals.  Sold as is.
